<br>
So US will probably say that Euro-guilds have an unfair time advantage on big mobs and things like that. <br>
<br>
To not have a rotation makes it VERY hard for some guilds to even have a shot at a big mob and will cause a lot of irritation in the long run.<br>
<br>
