<br>
New and somewhat unexplored zones, sure, they should be ffa until a reasonable amount of knowledge exists on the server giving the guilds that feel that they sacrifice time and effort to gain unknown knowledge should be rewarded more than the ones that just read the spoiler sites and waltz in and claim their spot. How long this ffa period should be should be discussed imho. <br>
<br>
ffa is a bit like anarchy for me, there needs to be a lot of consensus to implement rotations and such but in the long run I believe its for the benefit of all. Takes a lot of diplomacy....<br>
<br>
Anyway these are some of my thoughts.<br>
